	* lib/tempfile.rb: Embed Rdoc style comments.

	* lib/tempfile.rb: Add length as an alias for size.

	* lib/tempfile.rb: Add Tempfile#close!() as a shorthand for
	  Tempfile#close(true).

	* lib/tempfile.rb: Add Tempfile#{unlink,delete}().

